---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Card from '../components/Card.astro';
---

<Layout title="Dr. G-Mishmah">
	<main class="h-screen bg-slate-100">
		<section id="intro" class="w-full h-3/5 bg-cover bg-no-repeat bg-[url('/imgs/landscape_sunset.jpg')] flex flex-col text-center justify-center  border-t-2 border-t-amber-900">
			<div class="flex flex-col space-y-6 bg-black/60 py-24">
				<h1 class="text-7xl font-bold bg-gradient-to-l bg-clip-text text-transparent from-20% via-sky-400 from-sky-400 to-70% to-amber-100">
					Welcome to <span class="decoration-amber-900 dark:decoration-blue-500 underline">Dr. G-Mishmah</span>
				</h1>
				<h2 class="text-3xl text-slate-100 font-semibold">
					a novelist, a writer, a mathematician, a magician
				</h2>
			</div>
		</section>
		
		<section id="points" class="w-full h-auto bg-slate-100 flex flex-row items-stretch justify-evenly py-12">
			<card class="w-1/5 flex relative flex-col space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">
					Who is <br/>G-Mishmah?
				</h1>
				<p class="text-base font-semibold pr-4 border-r-2 border-amber-600">
					G-Mishmah (Elwood G. Edwards) is... Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Tenetur veniam hic eos tempora explicabo beatae odio commodi cum, quas eius nemo ut officia omnis? Sed.''
				</p>
				<a href="/about" class="text-center px-1.5 py-2 border-2 border-slate-100 bg-amber-600 text-slate-100 transition duration-150 focus:bg-slate-100 focus:text-amber-600 hover:border-amber-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-amber-600">
					About Author
				</a>  
			</card>

			<card class="w-1/5 flex relative flex-col space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">
					What are <br/>His Works?
				</h1>
				<p class="text-base font-semibold pr-4 border-r-2 border-amber-600">
					G-Mishmah writes with an intent focus on... Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Eum minima quaerat maiores ab nam ducimus beatae vel accusamus, dignissimos dolor.
				</p>

				<a href="/works" class="absolute bottom-0 w-full text-center px-1.5 py-2 border-2 border-slate-100 bg-amber-600 text-slate-100 transition duration-150 focus:bg-slate-100 focus:text-amber-600 hover:border-amber-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-amber-600">
					View Works
				</a>  
			</card>

			<card class="w-1/5 flex relative flex-col space-y-6">
				<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600">
					Why write<br/>the Novels?
				</h1>
				<p class="text-base font-semibold pr-4 border-r-2 border-amber-600">
					G-Mishmah really loves... Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur adipisicing elit. Placeat eius doloribus consequatur eaque. Blanditiis doloremque expedita alias voluptate quia facilis.
				</p>
				<a href="/blog" class="absolute bottom-0 w-full text-center px-1.5 py-2 border-2 border-slate-100 bg-amber-600 text-slate-100 transition duration-150 focus:bg-slate-100 focus:text-amber-600 hover:border-amber-600 hover:bg-slate-100 hover:text-amber-600">
					Read Blog
				</a>  
			</card>

			
		</section>

		<section id="content" class="flex flex-col px-24 py-8 bg-gradient-to-tr bg-opacity-20 from-amber-600 to-amber-300">
			{/* Header #1 - Works
					Edit components/Card.astro with MambaUI
					and give attr for title= and src= */}
				<article id="homepage-works" class="h-1/2 flex flex-col">
					<h1 id="homepage-works-header" class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-100 mb-4">
						Works of G-Mishmah
					</h1>

					<div class="flex flex-row space-x-4 | border-t-2 border-t-slate-100 p-4" id="homepage-works-content">
						<Card imageSrc='/covers/multicolored_dreams.jpg' imageAlt='Multicolored Dreams'
						type="novel" 
						title="Dreams are remarkable lenses for introspectionâ€”and Multicolored Dreams are the best kind." 
						body="Listen to the arts." />
					</div>
				</article>
			
			
			{/* Header #2 - Blog
				Edit components/Card.astro with MambaUI
				and give attr for title= and src= */}
		</section>
	</main>
</Layout>


